<h2>Time to make your first comment.</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Commenting</strong> helps us build a database of open peer review.</li>
  <li>Most Journal Lab discussion is <strong>focused on figures</strong>, like in a journal club.</li>
  <li>You can choose to <strong>provide your name</strong> or <strong>be anonymous.</strong></li>
  <li>Our community keeps comments professional and focused on the figures being discussed.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Here's how to comment:</h3>
<div class="row">
<div id="step3Carousel" class="carousel slide span5">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#step3Carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#step3Carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#step3Carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ol>
  <!-- Carousel items -->
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="active item">
      <%= image_tag 'http://s3.amazonaws.com/j.lab-images/static/step3_1.png' %>
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h4>What's the last interesting paper that you read?</h4>
        <p>Locate a paper using your feeds or the search bar in the upper right corner.</p>
        <p>Leaving comments on this paper will contribute to the scientific community and build your reputation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <%= image_tag 'http://s3.amazonaws.com/j.lab-images/static/step3_2.png' %>
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h4>Add Figures If Necessary</h4>
        <p>Sometimes you may need to help out by letting us know the number of figures in a paper. We really appreciate it!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <%= image_tag 'http://s3.amazonaws.com/j.lab-images/static/step3_3.png' %>
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h4>Click "Leave a Comment"</h4>
        <p>We'll provide the figure images when we can.</p>
        <p>You are also welcome to upload figures from open access journals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <%= image_tag 'http://s3.amazonaws.com/j.lab-images/static/step3_4.png' %>
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h4>Give Your High-Level Opinion</h4>
        <p>Click a badge to give your thoughts as a high level (e.g. "I'm Skeptical", "Interesting Hypothesis.")</p>
        <p>You can select more than one badge or make your own.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <%= image_tag 'http://s3.amazonaws.com/j.lab-images/static/step3_5.png' %>
      <div class="carousel-caption">
        <h4>Optional: Explain your Comment</h4>
        <p>If you like, enter a few sentences to explain your opinion.</p>
        <p>We'll notify everyone tracking this paper on their feeds, so people from your field will be drawn into the discussion.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item text-center">
      <br>
      <h2>Try it out!</h2>
        What's the last interesting paper that you read?
        <br>
      <br>
      <%= form_tag('/lookup', :method => "get") do  %>
          <%= text_field_tag(:search, "Discuss any paper on PubMed.", :onfocus =>  "if(this.value == 'Discuss any paper on PubMed.') { this.value = ''; }", :class => "inputSearch searchreset" ) %>
          <p><%= submit_tag "Search", :class => 'btn-tiny btn-primary round', :style => "vertical-align: top; margin-top: 2px;"%></p>
      <% end %>
      <div class="carousel-caption text-left">
        <h4>Let's leave your first comment!</h4>
        <p>Once you get the hang of it, commenting takes 15 seconds.</p>
        <p>Openly sharing your opinions builds your reputation and contributes to a better ecosystem of scientific communication.</p>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>
  <!-- Carousel nav -->
  <a class="carousel-control left" href="#step3Carousel" data-slide="prev">&lsaquo;</a>
  <a class="carousel-control right" href="#step3Carousel" data-slide="next">&rsaquo;</a>
</div>
</div>